Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:26.80,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}思い描いてるイメージより遙か向こう側へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:36.93,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}創り上げていく真実はまだ遠く…果てない旅路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:41.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}お互いのプライドを研ぎ澄ませようぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:44.40,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}言葉なんて飾りは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:46.78,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}開けさせりゃいい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:53.87,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}打つかり合い 磨かれていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:56.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}Rolling Stone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:58.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}出逢いはSHOCKWAVE！SHOCKWAVE！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.79,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}まだ知らない世界へ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:03.96,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}歩き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}無謀な挑戦者さ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.88,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}手にした刃で明日を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.72,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}切り拓けばいいんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:14.04,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}誰かのもんじゃない…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:17.77,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}自分だけのSTORY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:24.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}'Cause we're still ROUGH DIAMONDS on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:26.80,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}向着比心中描绘的图景更远的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:36.93,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}一步一步前进 真实还很遥远 旅途漫漫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:41.90,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}将彼此的自尊磨个透亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.15,0:02:44.40,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}语言什么的装饰品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.40,0:02:46.78,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}就不用去管了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:53.87,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}互相碰撞 不断磨练
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:56.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)\an8}Rolling Stone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:58.96,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}相遇就是SHOCKWAVE！SHOCKWAVE！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:01.79,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}向着未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:03.96,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}开始前行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:06.46,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}无谋的挑战者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.46,0:03:08.88,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}就用手中的刀刃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:11.72,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}去开拓明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.84,0:03:14.04,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}不是任何其他人的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:17.77,OP-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}是只属于自己的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.82,0:03:24.19,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(30,30)}{\an8}'Cause we're still ROUGH DIAMONDS on the road!
